T-Rex 0.18.10
* Add optional --no-strict-ssl parameter to disable certificate validation for SSL connections
* Change --fork-at parameter syntax to the following:
    Epoch number: <algo_name>=epoch:<epoch_number> (eg: --fork-at etchash=epoch:390 <-- use this one for upcoming ETC hardfork).
    Block number: <algo_name>=block:<block_number> (eg: --fork-at x16rv2=block:6526421).
    Time:  <algo_name>=time:<YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SS>. Time must be set in UTC+0.
